eles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They filmed part of the stunt in Los Angeles back in March.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.338183924282408e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People spotted Tom Cruise scaling the Hollywood sign and believed at the time that he was filming a commercial.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 1663, \"end\": 1677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flying drones captured the moment, but few realised that it was part of a grand Olympic-themed project.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sources revealed that Cruise inspired the stunt with his desire to create a memorable bridge between the two Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He reportedly pitched the concept to the International Olympic Committee, eager to bring his unique flair to the event.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2009, \"end\": 2040, \"title\": \"http://